data.title: Yul Edochie, Daddy Freeze, others congratulate Nigerian celebrity, Radiogad on birth of baby
data.meta_description: Media personality and influencer, Destiny Ezeyim, popularly known as Radigad has welcomed a baby girl with his British lover.
